title: Classic Beyond Meat® Meatballs with Spaghetti and Parmesan
description: Our spaghetti and meatballs taste just like Nonna's, but take a fraction of the time! The secret to these meatballs is swapping ground beef for Beyond Meat® and pairing them with a homemade tomato sauce that keeps the dish flavourful.

